                        <condition key="good">The Ms. reveals traces of extensive use.
 Many
                           fols. are worn and stained with dirt.
 The black ink is partly faded
                           (or possibly is of a different colour than the standard black?).
                           Holes have been amended, e.g., <locus target="#14">14</locus>.
 Many
                           fols. are held together with one stitch repairs.
 f. 7 was possibly
                           added later to substitute the lost leaf. <note>The quality and hue of the
                              black ink differs greatly throughout the Ms.</note>
                        </condition>
